</td>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;width:100%;padding:0px;padding:0.25em 0; line-height:1.4em; width:auto;;background:#f7f7f7;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em"><span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Dolby_Digital" title="Dolby Digital">AC-3</a> (<a href="/wiki/Surround_sound" title="Surround sound">5.1</a>)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/MPEG_Multichannel" title="MPEG Multichannel">MPEG Multichannel</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Pulse-code_modulation" title="Pulse-code modulation">PCM</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Linear_pulse_code_modulation" title="Linear pulse code modulation">LPCM</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Advanced_Audio_Coding" title="Advanced Audio Coding">AAC</a></span></div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height:2px">
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="navbox-group" style=";padding-left:0em;padding-right:0em;width:12.0em; background:lavender; font-weight:normal;;">
<div style="padding:0em 0.75em;">Hidden signals</div>
</td>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;width:100%;padding:0px;padding:0.25em 0; line-height:1.4em; width:auto;;background:transparent;;" class="navbox-list navbox-even">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em"><span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Closed_captioning" title="Closed captioning">Captioning</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Teletext" title="Teletext">Teletext</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/DVB-CPCM" title="DVB-CPCM">CPCM</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Broadcast_flag" title="Broadcast flag">Broadcast flag</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Active_Format_Descriptor" title="Active Format Descriptor" class="mw-redirect">AFD</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Electronic_program_guide" title="Electronic program guide">EPG</a></span></div>
