Hierarchical modulation: multi-resolution constellation (16QAM and 64QAM)<br />
Guard interval: 1/32, 1/16, 1/8 &amp; 1/4 of <a href="/wiki/OFDM" title="OFDM" class="mw-redirect">OFDM</a> symbol<br />
Two modes: 2k and 8k <a href="/wiki/Fast_Fourier_Transform" title="Fast Fourier Transform" class="mw-redirect">FFT</a></td>
<td><a href="/wiki/BST-COFDM" title="BST-COFDM" class="mw-redirect">BST-COFDM</a> with 13 frequency segments<br />
<a href="/wiki/DQPSK" title="DQPSK" class="mw-redirect">DQPSK</a>, QPSK, 16QAM and 64QAM<br />
Hierarchical modulation: choice of three different modulations on each segment<br />
Guard interval: 1/32, 1/16, 1/8 &amp; 1/4 of OFDM symbol<br />
Three modes: 2k, 4k and 8k FFT</td>
</tr>
